This archive contains the scripts, pattern to generate benchmarks for the paper submission for FMCAD 2018:

  Jianwen Li, Kristin Y. Rozier and Moshe Y. Vardi: 
  			Evaluating the Satisfiability of Mission-Time LTL: A Bounded MTL Over Naturals
 
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Files Description:
===========================

|-- generateRandomFormulas_MTLmax.pl/   		 The script to generate the random and random0 formulas. 
|                                                See the parameter information in the script.
|						
|-- random/   		         The directory of generated random formulas. 
|						
|
|-- random0/   		         The directory of generated random0 formulas.
|						
|
|-- pattern/   		         The directory of generated pattern formulas.
|						
|

